commit.message:
Merge Transforms branch to develop (#368)

* AosToSoa and SoaToAos transforms support
- block dim 16, 32, 64, 128, 256
- VW=2, 4, 8, 16

* Refactor vector ordering utilities into separate file. Optimize sub-dword vector re-ordering.

* Refactor vector_util interface. Add unit tests

* Update vector util description with 4 element examples

* Add unit tests
- vector util
- pack util
- transforms

* use vector_generator instead of unroll
* Cache given opCtrl code when applying cross lane ops to vectors. 
* Support F64 cross-lane ops
- DPP
- Swizzle
- Permute
- Blend

* Enable new large block (blockDim > 32, VW = max)  layouts in rocWMMA
- Refactor ColInlineVW to follow prioritize VWSegs->BlockKSegs->BlockDimSegs. 
- Update ColOrthoVW with consistent notations.
- Update inline docs.
- Added WaveCount support to the applyLayout function
- Update perf samples with new layouts

* Fixup compiler / validation on gfx11

* Cleanup and fixes
- delete dead code dppElement
- fixed validation
- remove various commented out code
- added inline documentation


---------

Co-authored-by: David Langbehn <dlangbeh@amd.com>
Co-authored-by: Meena Karunanidhi <mkarunan@amd.com>
Co-authored-by: Chris Millette <chris.millette@amd.com>
